Child model, Mildred Odige has won the international Model of the year category at the Star kids awards in Lagos, The five- year- old model, who is the daughter of publisher, LA Mode magazine, Sandra Odige also has a book reading club called ’’Mildred Reading and Talent Club for Kids’’ aims at developing reading culture and unleashing kids potentials. Born to Delta State parents, Mildred loves, reading , playing , sports (running) watching cartoons, dancing, fashion ,taking pictures and modelling in general, she has modelled for different brands and done shoots. Mildred is open to more opportunities as she is available and willing to represent brands responsibly.